Introduction

Na Go Eun, also known as Goeun, is a South Korean singer and dancer signed with RBW. She is the Main Vocalist, Lead Dancer, and Center of the girl group PURPLE KISS. She rose to fame after joining Mnet’s hit survival show, Produce 48 where she finished 29th.

She debuted with PURPLE KISS on March 15, 2021, with the mini album “INTO VIOLET”, with the title track “Ponzona”.
